OL,3,CBusinesses approve plans for a
OL,4,CCarlisle BID
OL,6,FCarlisle business owners have voted in
OL,7,Ffavour of plans to introduce a
OL,8,FBusiness Improvement District to the
OL,9,Fcity.
OL,11,FBusiness Improvement Districts, or
OL,12,FBIDs, can be found across the country
OL,13,Fin cities like York and towns in our
OL,14,Fregion like Kendal and Penrith.
OL,16,FBIDs are partnerships which involve
OL,17,Fbusinesses in local activities and can
OL,18,Fprovide extra services in an area,
OL,19,Fsuch as additional safety or cleaning
OL,20,Fmeasures.
