OL,3,CBusinesses approve plans for a
OL,4,CCarlisle BID
OL,6,FThey are funded through a charge on
OL,7,Fall eligible business rate payers,
OL,8,Fwhich is levied in addition to their
OL,9,Fbusiness rates bill.
OL,11,FIn Carlisle, 234 votes on the plans
OL,12,Fwere cast, representing a turnout of
OL,13,F24.7%.
OL,15,F128 votes were cast in favour of the
OL,16,FBID, with 106 votes against, and 2
OL,17,Frejected ballots.
