OL,3,CBusinesses approve plans for a
OL,4,CCarlisle BID
OL,6,FFor the plans to go ahead, it needed
OL,7,Fto achieve both a majority of votes in
OL,8,Fterms of the number of ballots, and in
OL,9,Fterms of the rateable value of the
OL,10,Fbusinesses.
OL,12,FIn this vote, the total rateable value
OL,13,Fof the businesses voting in favour
OL,14,Freached #7,477,750, while the rateable
OL,15,Fvalue of all businesses voting
OL,16,Ftotalled #11,509,550.
OL,18,FThe vote means that Carlisle's new
OL,19,FBusiness Improvement District will be
OL,20,Fin force from February of next year
OL,21,Funtil January 31, 2031.
